    Create a full-width banner section with customizable text content (title, subtitle, description, button) that can be positioned vertically. Include an animated play button icon that opens a YouTube video in a popup modal when clicked. Add comprehensive customization settings for content positioning, styling options, and video URL configuration. The section should be responsive and include smooth animations for the play button and popup functionality.

